summary: It All Started With The Laptop Slam
title: It All Started With The Laptop Slam
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2wMw1lt

by Kateis_Cakeis

BAKER
Steve Rogers was an interesting man. His life is one shrouded in secrecy. However, in the last few years, well kept secrets have been unearthed. Amongst the interviews with the surviving Howling Commandos and interviews with those who knew Rogers and his best friend, Bucky Barnes, back when they lived in Brooklyn. Now, there are many questions. In this programme, I aim to answer a few. The relationship between Rogers and his best friend is heavily debated, in this episode, we will find out how true the rumours are.

–
When a certain someone goes digging into the media of the past, they realise just how rife homophobia was over the years. Especially towards once close friends.

caption: Peter Quill getting angry at Thanos was totally an appropriate reaction. I mean the world took everything away from him. His mother. His father. His daddy. His walkman. And now the the love of his life? Hell I personally think Flawed characters are better and more concrete than normal ones
